{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Those that couldn't walk, they were just dumped on the truck and taken away to Birkenau to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And here I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I was in this group, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this French doctor came, and he yanked me out of bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He grabbed my card from the bed, because you know, they had a card on the bed, and you know, they just collected the cards, and bingo, you were gone.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he took me out, and he took me downstairs to the operating room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he gave me a white smock, and he said that you will be cleaning up the operating room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was very thankful, you know, that he did this to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I realized what he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you know, he had no-- had they taken me, I would have been gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I couldn't resist this, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So here I was in the operating room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I became the cleaner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was cleaning the floors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was cleaning the walls with disinfectant, and I was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I kept this place in tip top shape, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I really enjoyed doing what I was doing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, it gave me a new lease on life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The first thing that happened to me that I was able to clean my clothes, because after every operation, I was taking all the bloody gowns and sheets and everything to the laundry, you know, to clean.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And once you had a position like that-- so I sort of-- my level sort of went up, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, I became sort of a-- not quite a prominent, you know, but I was an assistant in the operating room, you see.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
